  <brief_title>Study of Bacteria on Mood and Bowel Symptoms in Patients With Irritable Bowel Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study of Probiotic Bifidobacterium Longum (B. Longum) on Mood and Bowel Symptoms in Patients With Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS).</official_title>
